---
title: Quick Fragrant Beef and Mushroom Stir-Fry with Pak Choi and Rice
description: A fast favourite, stir-frying is the perfect method to build flavour and cook quickly! This Quick Fragrant Beef and Mushroom Stir-Fry will be on your table in less than 25 minutes.
